h, R.P., Qualitative and quantitative analysis of snow parameters using passive microwave remote sensing (2005) J. Indian Soc. Remote Sens., 33 (3), pp. 381-393; Nghiem, S.V., Steffen, K., Neumann, G., Huff, R., Mapping of ice layer extent and snow accumulation in the percolation zone of the Greenland ice sheet (2005) J. Geophys. Res., 110, pp. 1-13; Nogues-Bravo, D., Araujo, M.B., Errea, M.P., Martinez-Rica, J.P., Exposure of global mountain systems to climate warming during the 21st Century (2007) Global Environmental Change, 17 (3-4), pp. 420-428. , DOI 10.1016/j.gloenvcha.2006.11.007, PII S0959378006000926; Ohmura, A., Completing the world glacier inventory (2009) Ann. Glaciol., 50 (53), pp. 144-148; Pu, Z., Xu, L., MODIS/Terra observed snow cover over the Tibet Plateau: Distribution, variation and possible connection with the East Asian summer monsoon (EASM) (2009) Theor. Appl. Climatol., 97 (3-4), pp. 265-278; Radić, V., Hock, R., Regional and global volumes of glaciers derived from statistical upscaling of glacier inventory data (2010) J. Geophys. Res., 115, pp. F01010; Ramage, J.M., Isacks, B.L., Determination of melt-onset and refreeze timing on southeast Alaskan icefields using SSM/I diurnal amplitude variations (2002) Annals of Glaciology, 34, pp. 391-398. , Papers from the Fourth International Symposium on Remote Sensing in Glaciology held in Colleg Park, Maryland, USA, 3-8 June 2001; Raup, B., Racoviteanu, A., Khalsa, S.J.S., Helm, C., Armstrong, R., Arnaud, Y., The GLIMS geospatial glacier database: A new tool for studying glacier change (2007) Global and Planetary Change, 56 (1-2), pp. 101-110. , DOI 10.1016/j.gloplacha.2006.07.018, PII S0921818106001597, Climate Change Impacts on Mountain Glaciers and Permafrost; Schiermeier, Q., Glacier estimate is on thin ice (2010) Nature, 463 (7279), p. 276; Sharp, M., Wang, L., A five-year record of summer melt on Eurasian Arctic ice caps (2009) J. Climatol., 22 (1), pp. 133-145; Shrestha, A.B., Wake, C.P., Maye